title: PwnageTool_2.2.1.dmg
description:
This is a release of PwnageTool that fixes a bug that was present in PwnageTool 2.2.1, for more details please the specific blog post at http://blog.iphone-dev.org/post/61060174/the-man-from-delmonte-he-say-yes

PwnageTool 2.2.1 is a Mac based iPhone firmware creation tool for creating custom ipsw/firmware for the 1st gen iPod Touch, iPhone and iPhone 3G. This version supports the 2.2 firmware from Apple. For full details (which are often updated) visit the iphone DevTeam blog. http://blog.iphone-dev.org
